      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Muhammad, from one of his companions, from Al Washha, from Al Husayn Bin Al Mukhtar, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Do not enshroud the deceased in black’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "11. Ali ibn Muhammad has narrated from certain persons of his people from al-Washsha’ from al-Husayn ibn al-Mukhtar who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘A deceased is not shrouded in black.’” "
        ]
